Rocky Linux的首个候选版本发布于2021年4月30日，首个正式版本发布于2021年6月21日。Rocky Linux 8将提供支持至2029年5月。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://forums.rockylinux.org/t/what-is-eol-of-rl8/3316/3|title="What is EOL of RL8"|publisher=Brian Clemens|date=June 30, 2021|access-date=August 5, 2021|archive-date=2021-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025205539/https://forums.rockylinux.org/t/what-is-eol-of-rl8/3316/3}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
2020年12月8日，红帽公司宣布，他们将停止开发[[CentOS|CentOS]]，而在此之前CentOS一直作为红帽企业Linux的生产型分支及下游版本，此后他们将转而开发该操作系统的一个更新的上游开发变种，即 “CentOS Stream”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Red Hat resets CentOS Linux and users are angry|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/red-hat-resets-centos-linux-and-users-are-angry/|accessdate=2020-12-22|last=Vaughan-Nichols|first=Steven J.|work=ZDNet|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220409034310/https://www.zdnet.com/article/red-hat-resets-centos-linux-and-users-are-angry/}}</ref>。为此，CentOS的创始人Gregory Kurtzer宣布，他将重新启动一个项目，以实现CentOS的原始目标。该名字来源于CentOS早期的联合创始人Rocky McGaugh<ref>{{Cite web|title=Goodbye CentOS, hello Rocky Linux|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/goodbye-centos-hello-rocky-linux/|accessdate=2020-12-22|last=Vaughan-Nichols|first=Steven J.|work=ZDNet|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220420021400/https://www.zdnet.com/article/goodbye-centos-hello-rocky-linux/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=CentOS Linux is dead—and Red Hat says Stream is “not a replacement”|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2020/12/centos-shifts-from-red-hat-unbranded-to-red-hat-beta/|accessdate=2020-12-22|date=2020-12-10|last=Salter|first=Jim|work=Ars Technica|language=en-us|archive-date=2022-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220316140809/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2020/12/centos-shifts-from-red-hat-unbranded-to-red-hat-beta/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=As CentOS 8 Is About To Die, Its Creator Gave Birth To Rocky Linux|url=https://fossbytes.com/centos-8-about-to-die-creator-new-rocky-linux/|accessdate=2020-12-22|date=2020-12-11|last=Kumar|first=Sarvottam|work=Fossbytes|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206205952/https://fossbytes.com/centos-8-about-to-die-creator-new-rocky-linux/}}</ref>。在发布后两天内Rocky Linux已经在GitHub上获得了超过两千六百个点赞，而至12月12日，根据GitHub趋势功能显示该项目<ref name=":0">{{Citation|title=rocky-linux/rocky|url=https://github.com/rocky-linux/rocky|publisher=Rocky Linux|date=2020-12-22|accessdate=2020-12-22|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210191639/https://github.com/rocky-linux/rocky}}</ref>已成为[[GitHub|GitHub]]上最热门的仓库<ref>{{Cite web|title=Trending repositories on GitHub today · GitHub|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212220049/https://github.com/trending|accessdate=2020-12-22|date=2020-12-12|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>。

2020年12月22日，RokyLinux的社区管理员Jordan Pisaniello宣布目标将在2021年3月至5月之间发布初始版本。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/rocky-linux-first-release-is-coming-in-q2-2021-say-developers |title=Rocky Linux: First release is coming in Q2 2021 say developers |author=Tung, Liam |publisher=[[ZDNet|ZDNet]] |date=December 24, 2020 |access-date=January 25, 2021 |archive-date=2021-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211111060936/https://www.zdnet.com/article/rocky-linux-first-release-is-coming-in-q2-2021-say-developers/ }}</ref>2021年1月20日，宣布将在2月底前向公众提供测试储存库，并在2021年3月底发布候选版本。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Rocky-Linux-Aiming-For-Q2 |title=Rocky Linux Making Progress Towards Their First Release In Q2 As A Free RHEL Alternative |author=Larabel, Michael |publisher=Phoronix |date=January 20, 2021 |access-date=January 25, 2021 |archive-date=2022-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121223223/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item }}</ref>但是发布日期在这之后宣布延迟，<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-03-31|title=Community Update - March 2021|url=https://forums.rockylinux.org/t/community-update-march-2021/2232|access-date=2021-03-31|website=Rocky Linux Discourse|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629154554/https://forums.rockylinux.org/t/community-update-march-2021/2232}}</ref>直到2021年4月30日，首个候选版本才正式发布。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-04-30|title=Rocky Linux 8.3 RC1 Available Now|url=https://rockylinux.org/news/rocky-linux-8-3-rc1-release/|access-date=2021-05-01|website=Rocky Linux|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211011121804/https://rockylinux.org/news/rocky-linux-8-3-rc1-release/}}</ref>2021年6月4日，宣布8.4版作为第二个候选版本，这也是稳定版之前的最后一个版本。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-06-04|title=Rocky Linux 8.4 RC1 Available Now|url=https://rockylinux.org/news/rocky-linux-8-4-rc1-release/|access-date=2021-06-12|website=Rocky Linux|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220509224812/https://rockylinux.org/news/rocky-linux-8-4-rc1-release/}}</ref>2021年6月21日，Rocky Linux 8.4的稳定版发布，<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-06-21|title=Rocky Linux 8.4 Available Now|url=https://forums.rockylinux.org/t/rocky-linux-8-4-available-now/3015/1|access-date=2021-06-21|website=Rocky Linux|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628052414/https://forums.rockylinux.org/t/rocky-linux-8-4-available-now/3015/1}}</ref>代号为“Green Obsidian”。<ref name="Green Obsidian">{{cite web|date=2021-05-24|title=add version code (b39e0955)|url=https://git.rockylinux.org/original/rpms/rocky-release/-/commit/b39e0955441c84f1c47748714f7ca0c99dea8022#be10d0b0a83782a427f0ed59e87fd16abcbe797e_10_10|website=Rocky Linux GitLab Server|language=en|author=Abel, Louis|access-date=2021-06-22|archive-date=2021-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628182811/https://git.rockylinux.org/original/rpms/rocky-release/-/commit/b39e0955441c84f1c47748714f7ca0c99dea8022#be10d0b0a83782a427f0ed59e87fd16abcbe797e_10_10}}</ref>

== 迁移 ==
Rocky Linux计划在CentOS 8寿命结束前发布CentOS的替代品。其也将能在x86-64和基于[[ARM架構|ARM]]的处理器上运行<ref name=":0" />，CentOS用户只需运行一个命令就能将他们的操作系统转换为Rocky Linux。

